This week Raiza calls Carlos out on his use of emoji’s. This inspires a bigger conversation on how everyone uses emoji’s differently, the crew talks about their favorite emoji’s to use, and Tony brings up Furries (sí, Furries!). Then the amazingly funny comedian, Rhea Butcher stops by to chat about their upcoming stand up tour, showing up for people, and their roll as a villain on Good Trouble. Finally, Rhea dusts off their improv skills and jumps in on the fun. 
